(170, 4, 'Hyderabadi\n              Biryani ', '350 gms Basmati Rice <br>\n         200 gms Potatoes <br>\n         200 gms Carrots <br>\n         100 gms Onions <br>\n         4 Green Chilies <br>\n         30 gms Ginger <br>\n         20 gms Garlic <br>\n         1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder<br>\n         1 tsp R', '<li>Wash and soak the basmati rice for half an hour. Drain the water.\n            Put the rice, some more water and add half the whole garam masala\n            and salt in a pan. </li>\n          <li>Bring the rice to a boil and cook until the rice is done', '2013-03-17 09:25:14', '2013-03-17 09:25:14'),
